  • public class GenericThingProviderTest4
extends JavaOSGiTest
    Test class for the GenericThingProvider. It focuses on the XML processing (i.e. ThingType loading) and verifies that the loading of Things gets delayed until the XML processing is completed.
    Author:
    Simon Kaufmann - Initial contribution and API.
